name: LOVE 22 - 01
description:
LOVE is an audio-visual project that consists of:

- "LOVE", music nft (first mint under my own smart contract)

- LOVE Music video (second mint under my own smart contract)

- 22 objkts minted on Tezos in editions of 2, priced at 2.22 tez

- Collaborative Project: I will share the music stems with musicians who request them and there will be a 2nd drop with the LOVE remixes, splitting each remix 50/50 on the blockchain. * To request stems, head out to my website --> vjdeliria.com 

 
The LOVE project dropped on 22-2-22 and is dedicated to the two most important people in my life.

Connect on Twitter @VjDeliria and say hi :)
